Strructure as follow


Welcome Message 

Check data and two quick reply your ID / another ID

your_id

- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/user_check.php?messenger_id={{messenger user id}}
- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/{{messenger user id}}_data.json
- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/files_delete.php?messenger_id={{messenger user id}}
- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/tryagain.json

another_id

user input to get user_id
- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/user_check.php?messenger_id={{user_id}}
- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/{{user_id}}_data.json
- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/files_delete.php?messenger_id={{user_id}}	- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/tryagain.json

