delete_user

as per the policy you can delete only your data and one quick reply your ID

delete_you

Are you sure that you want to delete your data ?
quick reply with yes or no 
yes continue and no revert back to welcome message

- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/user_delete.php?messenger_id={{messenger user id}}
- http://chatfuelclone.atwebpages.com/showusers/{{messenger user id}}_data.json
